    <!--help center-->
    <div class="help-center">
        <h1 class="footer-title3">Help Center</h1><br>
        <h3>How can we help you?</h3><br>
        <p>Find answers to common questions and get support for any issues you encounter while using Ciniverse.</p><br>
        <hr><br>
        <h2>1. Getting Started</h2><br>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>How does Cineverse work?</strong><br>Simply tell us your mood or preferences, and we'll
            recommend movies that match your taste.</li><br>
            <li><strong>Do I need an account to use Cineverse?</strong><br>No, you can browse recommendations 
            without an account. However, creating an account lets you save favorites and get more personalized
            suggestions.</li><br>
        </ul>
        <hr><br>
        <h2>2. Movie Recommendations</h2><br>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>How are recommendations generated?</strong><br>Our system analyzes your preferences, 
            watch history, and trending films to suggest the best options for you.</li><br>
            <li><strong>Can I filter recommendations?</strong><br>Yes! You can filter by genre, release year,
            rating, and more to find exactly what you're looking for.</li><br>
        </ul>
        <hr><br>
        <h2>3. Troubleshooting & Support</h2><br>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Why am I not getting any recommendations?</strong><br>Try refreshing the page or 
            updating your preferences. If the issue continues, contact us for support.</li><br>
            <li><strong>I found incorrect information about a movie. What should I do?</strong><br>Let us
            know by clicking the "Report" button on the movie page.</li><br>
            <li><strong>How do I contact support?</strong><br>You can reach through out 
            <strong>Contact Us</strong> page.</li><br>
        </ul>
        <hr><br>
        <h2>4. Privacy & Account Settings</h2><br>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Is my data safe with Cineverse?</strong><br>Absolutely! We take privacy seriously
            and don't share your data with third parties. See our 
            <a href="privacy_policy" style="color:rgb(234, 141, 234);">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</li><br>
            <li><strong>Can I delete my account?</strong><br>Yes, go to you <strong>Account Settings</strong>
            and select <strong>Delete Account</strong>. This will remove all your data permanently.</li><br>
        </ul>
        <hr><br>
        <h2>Still need help?</h2><br>
        <p>If you coundn't find what you were looking for, feel free to 
        <a href="contact_us" style="color: rgb(234, 141, 234);">Contact Us</a>. We're happy to assist you!</p>
    </div>

